-- CANADA RESEARCH ROUNDUP: -Polymet Mining Corp, Tricon Capital Group Inc 
-- 
-- Tue Sep 30, 2014 07:23AM EDT
-- None



Sept 30 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including Polymet Mining Corp  and Tricon Capital Group Inc , on Tuesday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Polymet Mining Corp <POM.TO>: CIBC starts with sector outperformer; price target C$2 * Tricon Capital Group Inc <TCN.TO>: Raymond James starts with outperform; C$9.50 target   Following is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Tuesday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.* Black Diamond Group Ltd <BDI.TO>: RBC cuts target to C$28 from C$34; rating outperform  * Black Diamond Group Ltd <BDI.TO>: Acumen cuts price target to C$32.50; rating buy * Concordia Healthcare Corp <CXR.TO>: TD Securities resumes coverage with buy rating * Fortis Inc <FTS.TO>: BMO raises target price to C$36 from C$34; rating market perform * Polymet Mining Corp <POM.TO>: CIBC starts with sector outperformer; price target C$2 * Temple Hotels <TPH.TO>: National Bank Financial cuts target price to C$5.75 from C$6 * Tricon Capital Group Inc <TCN.TO>: Raymond James starts with outperform; C$9.50 target  * Yamana Gold Inc <YRI.TO>: Paradigm Capital cuts target price to C$8 from C$9; rating hold